Meet Cocoa! This 3 year old female labrador retriever mix was transferred to our shelter from the Town of Brookhaven Animal Shelter, which is an overcrowded shelter on Long Island. Cocoa is now available for adoption and enjoying her day behind the front desk at SASF!

Cocoa is a snuggly, loving dog. Cocoa is a pleasure to walk on a leash and loves making new friends. While she doesn’t yet know many commands, Cocoa is eager to please and ready to learn. She also loves to receive belly rubs. Her perfect day would involve cuddling on the couch while you sip hot cocoa. Come meet this cozy girl today!
